  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 390°F/ Gas 6</p>\n<p>Put a large baking tray (or two) in the oven to heat up (this will stop the pizza bottoms from going soggy!)</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to a bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p>\n<p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp]</span><strong> cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the ends from the <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>, then finely slice</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>smoked bacon</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and pat the <strong>mozzarella</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong> (squeeze as much liquid out as you can!)</p>\n<p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> pizza bases</strong> to a baking tray (or two)</p>\n<p>Divide the <strong>tomato sauce </strong>between the <strong>pizza bases </strong>and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p>\n<p>Top with the<strong> torn mozzarella </strong>and dot the<strong> onion marmalade </strong>all over</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top with the <strong>sliced Brussels sprouts</strong> and <strong>chopped bacon</strong></p>\n<p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven for 13-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the bases are crisp – these are your <strong>Christmas bacon &amp; sprout pizzas</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and <strong>mayonnaise</strong> in a bowl – this is your<strong> mustard mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/christmas-bacon-and-sprout-pizza/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Christmas bacon &amp; sprout pizzas</strong> with the<strong> mustard mayo</strong> to the side</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
